data.description: Prepare to be amazed by this stunning corner lot in Sanford, FL! Upon arrival, you’ll notice the beautifully landscaped yard, with rubber mulch to ensure easy maintenance. Step inside to discover the welcoming, open floor plan with an expansive kitchen featuring a massive eat-in island; granite countertops and porcelain tile backsplash add a touch of elegance. All appliances, including the energy-efficient washer and dryer, come with the home. Added features to this home include built in Sonos surround sound system in the main living area and a holiday electrical package (Holiday lights are already installed and can be turned on by a simple light switch). Enjoy perfect temperatures on each floor with two thermostats. The 2019 build is bathed in natural light, creating a light and airy atmosphere. Upstairs, find the bedrooms and a spacious loft. The owner's suite boasts a tall, tray ceiling and a large double vanity in the en-suite. Don't miss the beautiful screened-in lanai for morning coffee or outdoor dinners. The backyard oasis includes extended pavers and plenty of green grass for your furry friend. The community offers a dog park, playground, and a COMMUNITY POOL in a rapidly growing, centrally located area with easy access to Orlando and Sanford amenities! Grocery shopping is a breeze, with a brand new Publix just minutes away. Schedule your showing today!
